Problem Statement Selected

HR Cost Intelligence / Meeting-to-Project Cost Attribution

Organizations lack visibility into how meeting time translates into real HR spend per project. Timesheets are manual and unreliable, while calendar data already captures where people spend their time. This problem requires connecting calendar meetings → AI-powered project attribution → employee cost mapping → executive dashboards and anomaly detection.



Project Description

HR Cost Intelligence Engine is an AI-powered FinOps platform that answers one critical business question: “What are our meetings actually costing us, and which projects are driving that spend?”

The platform automatically syncs Google Calendar meetings, uses AI (Google Gemini) to attribute each meeting to one or more projects, calculates cost using employee hourly rates, and surfaces everything on an executive dashboard — with anomaly flags, forecasts, and a voice-enabled AI assistant.

