Approach

1. Data ingestion





Google Calendar OAuth + hourly sync scheduler



Configurable sync window (7–90 days)



Demo mode with 17 seeded meetings (no OAuth required for judges)

2. AI attribution





Gemini AI classifies meetings to projects with confidence scores



Keyword fallback when API key is unavailable



Multi-project split support (allocationPct for cross-functional meetings)



Meetings below 70% confidence → review queue for human approval

3. Cost engine





Meeting Cost = duration × Σ(attendee hourly rates) × allocation %



ROI score heuristic per meeting



Role and department rollups for project drill-down

4. Intelligence layer





4-rule anomaly detection engine



Rule-based recommendations and 4-week cost forecasts



AI Copilot for natural-language Q&A with chart output



FinOps Assistant (floating chatbot) with text + voice — navigate app, sync calendar, export CSV

5. Governance





RBAC: ADMIN / HR / FINANCE / MANAGER / VIEWER



Salary rate masking by role



Full audit log for attribution overrides and exports



